arStrings.szText: What a dismal faithless existence. That’s the problem with you and the Horadrim. Such thinking always leads to hubris. And hubris leads to failure.
Lorath’s no stranger to it. Buried his own brother. Chased away the little one, that brat Neyrelle. Only comfort left for him is at the bottom of a bottle.
Tread carefully, wanderer. Judgment hungers for you both. And outside the city walls, not even our Reverend Mother will be able to stay its hand.
